             VISN1 Home Caribou Community Based Outpatient Clinic

   Photo of sign outside Caribou clinic VA Caribou CBOC
                                                    163 Van Buren Drive, Suite 6
                                                          Caribou, ME 04736
                                                        Phone: (207) 498-8785

                                                           Practice Hours:
                                                      8:00am - 4:30pm, Mon-Fri
                                                        For after hours care,
                                                     contact the Togus facility

                                          Directions

        The Caribou VA Clinic was the first of Togus' Community Based
   Outpatient Clinics, established in May 1987. The patient population has
    nearly doubled in the past year. Due to this increase in patients, we
   have expanded our staff to include 2 physicians, 1 Nurse Practitioner,
                2 Registered Nurses and 1 Health Technician.

                              SERVICES PROVIDED
                 Primary Care and Preventive Health Services
                     Health Promotion/Disease Prevention
                         Medical Benefits Counseling
                                 Dermatology
                                 Laboratory

                                KEY CONTACTS
                 Clinic Contact Point: Robert L. Shaw, M.D.
                            Togus Contact Point:

     Richard P. Corbin, M.D., Primary Care Service Line Manager

     Penelope Graham, N.P., CBOC Firm Manager

                                 DIRECTIONS
                      (Distance from Togus: 250 miles)

     Take Interstate 95 North to Houlton exit. Take a left off exit ramp
    onto U.S. Route 1. Stay on Route 1 past the Caribou Inn & Convention
     Center. Take a left at the light (appx. 2 miles past the Convention
    Center). Approximately 1/2 mile down the road is Cary Medical Center.
     You will see signs for VA Clinic as you take a right into hospital
                                  driveway.
